1. Decide which business to order from
    1a. Make sure they have good reviews
2. Decide which type of pizza to order
    2a. Look for specialty pizzas
3. Call the pizza place
4. Order the pizza
    4a. Pay over phone
    4b. Pay at door
5. Wait for delivery
    5a. Don't answer the door if your delivery man is wearing a mask and has an axe.
6. Greet delivery driver
7. See step 4b if necessary